Name: ControlledVocabularyID
Description: The ID of the code controlled vocabulary that the content was taken from.

Name: ControlledVocabularyAgencyName
Description: The name of the agency maintaining the controlledVocabulary.

Name: ControlledVocabularyVersionID
Description: The version number of the controlledVocabulary (default is 1.0).

Name: OtherValue
Description: If the value of the string is "Other" or the equivalent from the controlledVocabulary, this attribute can provide a more specific value not found in the codelist.

Name: ControlledVocabularySchemeURN
Description: If maintained within a scheme, the URN of the scheme containing the controlledVocabulary.
